00:31:14.419 --> 00:31:16.599
it had a impact in his life

00:31:16.599 --> 00:31:19.419
and it changed his profession.

00:31:19.419 --> 00:31:21.419
His profession changed.

00:31:21.419 --> 00:31:25.059
The Bible tells us that he was a publican,

00:31:25.059 --> 00:31:26.499
he was a tax collector,

00:31:26.579 --> 00:31:28.779
he's sitting at the receipt of custom,

00:31:28.779 --> 00:31:31.979
but we know that he's no longer going to fulfill,

00:31:31.979 --> 00:31:34.759
he's no longer going to be engaged

00:31:34.759 --> 00:31:36.219
in that line of work.

00:31:36.219 --> 00:31:40.819
He's now going to be an apostle.

00:31:40.819 --> 00:31:44.939
It's amazing.

00:31:44.939 --> 00:31:48.779
And we think about the specific call of Matthew.

00:31:48.779 --> 00:31:50.779
Again, this morning, in a general sense,

00:31:50.779 --> 00:31:52.419
God's calling you to follow Him,

00:31:52.419 --> 00:31:54.339
but for some, God is calling

00:31:54.819 --> 00:31:57.299
in a full-time capacity.

00:31:57.299 --> 00:32:01.579
