00:32:01.579 --> 00:32:03.539
to full-time ministry well before

00:32:03.539 --> 00:32:06.739
I ever got a call from Fellowship Baptist Church.

00:32:06.739 --> 00:32:08.259
I knew that God had called me,

00:32:08.259 --> 00:32:09.699
I had prepared in Bible college,

00:32:09.699 --> 00:32:12.019
I was surrendered to what the Lord would want

00:32:12.019 --> 00:32:14.219
and God had me working in churches,

00:32:14.219 --> 00:32:15.899
He had me working in the corporate world

00:32:15.899 --> 00:32:18.619
and I worked in the corporate world for years.

00:32:18.619 --> 00:32:20.619
And I remember as I worked in the corporate world

00:32:20.619 --> 00:32:22.019
wondering from time to time,

00:32:22.019 --> 00:32:23.939
Lord, when?

00:32:23.939 --> 00:32:26.619
You didn't forget about me.

00:32:26.619 --> 00:32:29.059
And I remember God making it abundantly clear

00:32:29.059 --> 00:32:33.059
that it was time.

00:32:33.059 --> 00:32:35.179
And Holly and I, we were surrendered.

00:32:35.179 --> 00:32:37.139
Lord, where do You want us?

00:32:37.139 --> 00:32:39.099
I remember going over to my parents' house

00:32:39.099 --> 00:32:41.699
and talking to them about coming to

00:32:41.699 --> 00:32:43.139
a church in Oakton, Virginia

00:32:43.139 --> 00:32:45.579
that was looking for a pastor.

00:32:45.579 --> 00:32:47.419
I remember the conversation.

00:32:47.419 --> 00:32:49.219
I remember them asking,

00:32:49.259 --> 00:32:52.059
are you guys alright financially to do that?

00:32:52.059 --> 00:32:54.219
Moms and dads are concerned about that.

00:32:54.219 --> 00:32:57.259
As they should be.

00:32:57.259 --> 00:33:00.259
We talked and we prayed.

00:33:00.259 --> 00:33:02.659
We're praying for the will of God.

00:33:02.659 --> 00:33:05.099
And I remember as some of you that were here then,

00:33:05.099 --> 00:33:08.299
you know the events and how it all worked out.

00:33:08.299 --> 00:33:11.499
It was amazing because for months

00:33:11.499 --> 00:33:14.339
after we knew it was time,

00:33:14.339 --> 00:33:17.379
there's really no opportunity.

00:33:17.379 --> 00:33:18.699
The counsel that I received was

00:33:18.699 --> 00:33:20.259
don't send a resume to anyone.

00:33:20.259 --> 00:33:21.379
God knows where you are

00:33:21.379 --> 00:33:23.619
and He knows where you need to be.

00:33:23.619 --> 00:33:25.499
And so we're just waiting on God.

00:33:25.499 --> 00:33:28.379
Asking God to open a door.

00:33:28.379 --> 00:33:30.299
Now for some of you that have the same kind of personality

00:33:30.299 --> 00:33:33.419
that I do, that's hard.

00:33:33.419 --> 00:33:36.219
Because sometimes we think we can help God.

00:33:36.219 --> 00:33:37.099
Right?

00:33:37.099 --> 00:33:38.739
If you have the kind of personality I have,

00:33:38.739 --> 00:33:39.699
you understand.

00:33:39.699 --> 00:33:41.899
You can relate.

00:33:41.899 --> 00:33:42.899
I was working in the corporate world.

00:33:42.899 --> 00:33:47.499
Everything was about networking.

00:33:47.499 --> 00:33:49.939
Or just trusting God.

00:33:49.939 --> 00:33:51.659
But when God opened the door,

00:33:51.659 --> 00:33:53.859
it was fast.

00:33:53.859 --> 00:33:56.459
Seriously, it was fast.

00:33:56.459 --> 00:34:01.179
