You're crazy.

00:34:14.259 --> 00:34:17.899
I'm not accepting your resignation.

00:34:17.899 --> 00:34:20.139
Now I didn't know that an employer could say

00:34:20.139 --> 00:34:21.139
they weren't going to accept.

00:34:21.139 --> 00:34:23.619
I didn't have any kind of contract.

00:34:23.619 --> 00:34:25.499
I'm not accepting your resignation.

00:34:25.499 --> 00:34:27.059
You need to go talk to.

00:34:27.059 --> 00:34:28.699
