00:34:28.699 --> 00:34:30.939
and the next boss and the next boss.

00:34:30.939 --> 00:34:34.259
Because they didn't want to accept my resignation.

00:34:34.259 --> 00:34:36.579
But God was changing my profession,

00:34:36.579 --> 00:34:41.619
quote unquote, if I could use that term this morning.

00:34:41.619 --> 00:34:43.019
And I remember sitting in the office

00:34:43.059 --> 00:34:47.259
and the guy that was four or five levels above me

00:34:47.259 --> 00:34:49.099
making all kinds of statements

00:34:49.099 --> 00:34:51.819
and where you could be in so many years

00:34:51.819 --> 00:34:54.379
and so on and so forth.

00:34:54.379 --> 00:34:55.539
What was he trying to do?

00:34:55.539 --> 00:34:59.979
He was trying to convince me to stay.

00:34:59.979 --> 00:35:01.219
Look at what the possibilities are.

00:35:01.219 --> 00:35:03.899
Look at what the opportunities are before you.

00:35:03.899 --> 00:35:05.699
I mean, the future's bright for you.

00:35:05.699 --> 00:35:07.779
Why would you do this?

00:35:07.779 --> 00:35:11.539
Because God called me.

00:35:11.539 --> 00:35:14.819
It was really kind of simple.

00:35:14.819 --> 00:35:17.819
Because I knew that God called me.

00:35:17.819 --> 00:35:20.699
And we see here for Matthew,

00:35:20.699 --> 00:35:22.779
his profession changed.

00:35:22.779 --> 00:35:24.539
