00:35:26.899 --> 00:35:29.659
as we go through the remainder of this little text

00:35:29.659 --> 00:35:30.899
of scripture this morning,

00:35:30.899 --> 00:35:32.819
this will be the truth for each of us

00:35:32.819 --> 00:35:35.499
whether we're speaking in a general sense

00:35:35.499 --> 00:35:37.179
