00:35:39.859 --> 00:35:43.659
or a full-time ministry type of situation of Matthew here,

00:35:43.659 --> 00:35:45.819
I want you to notice not only did his profession change,

00:35:45.819 --> 00:35:48.379
but his perspective changed.

00:35:48.379 --> 00:35:50.179
His perspective changed.

00:35:50.179 --> 00:35:52.219
See, I want you to think about Matthew just for a moment.

00:35:52.219 --> 00:35:55.019
I want you to think about how he viewed people.

