00:36:08.299 --> 00:36:09.699
He's collecting the taxes.

00:36:10.539 --> 00:36:12.139
He was levying the taxes.

00:36:12.139 --> 00:36:15.139
And we find that he's now going

00:36:15.139 --> 00:36:17.699
to have a change of perspective.

00:36:17.699 --> 00:36:18.539
Why?

00:36:18.539 --> 00:36:21.059
Because these people no longer are just the means

00:36:21.059 --> 00:36:24.219
by which I'm going to receive my wealth.

00:36:24.219 --> 00:36:27.459
These people are people that are in need of a savior.

