00:38:01.619 --> 00:38:03.219
That's a change of perspective.

00:38:03.219 --> 00:38:05.539
That's a change of priority.

00:38:05.539 --> 00:38:09.099
And as we're following the Lord Jesus Christ in our lives,

00:38:09.099 --> 00:38:10.459
as we understand that he said,

00:38:10.459 --> 00:38:13.859
follow me to each of us as his children,

00:38:13.859 --> 00:38:16.379
we're going to have a difference in our perspective

00:38:16.379 --> 00:38:19.539
and in our priorities as we're following Christ.

00:38:20.859 --> 00:38:22.779
