00:38:22.779 --> 00:38:25.819
and it came to pass as Jesus sat at meat in the house,

00:38:25.819 --> 00:38:27.099
behold, notice what it says,

00:38:27.099 --> 00:38:30.059
many publicans and sinners came

00:38:30.059 --> 00:38:33.019
